                               Context context)

        Information about the current playback

        Parameters:
        timestamp - Unix Millisecond Timestamp when data was fetched
        device - The device that is currently active
        progressMs - Progress into the currently playing track. Can be null (e.g. If private session is enabled this will be null).
        isPlaying - If something is currently playing.
        track - The currently playing track. Can be null (e.g. If private session is enabled this will be null).
        shuffleState - If shuffle is on or off
        context - A Context Object. Can be null (e.g. If private session is enabled this will be null).
